Feature Engineering:
- NumberItems: total rows of this visit
- WeekdayNumber: converted Mon-Sun to integers 0-6
- IsWeekday: if it is weekday / weekend
- Upc: used as int
- ScanCount, TotalScanCount: summed up ScanCount column for each visit
- DepartmentDescription: used dummy coding
- FinelineNumber: used as int

This is done from scratch and I have not read anybody else's solution. Only used XGBoost with the features above. I am still in the process of creating more features, and have not done any parameter tuning.
